content.rendered:
Directed by Ajay Bahl.

Written by Ajay Bahl.

Cast Akshaye Khanna(Tarun Saluja). Richa Chadha(Hiral Gandhi). Rahul Bhat(Rohan Khurana). Meera Chopra(Anjali Damle). Shriswara(Kainaz Khurana (as Shree Swara)). Kishore Kadam(Justice Madgaonkar). Kruttika Desai(Justice Indrani (as Krutika Desai)). Sandhya Mridul(Shilpa). Shrikant Yadav(PSI Kasle). Vibhawari Deshpande(ASI Manali). Shama Ninawe(Anjali’s Mother). Rajendra Shisatkar(Anjali’s Father (as Rajendra Shishatkar)). Anup Choudhary(Pramod). Shahnaaz Deshpande(Natasha Malhotra). Sahil Chaddha(Jasbir Walia (as Saahil Chadha)). Tanuka Laghate(Meera). Prajakta Wadaye(Savi). Narendra Karekar(Datta Shinde). Nishank Verma(Shekhar). Raviza Chauhan(Prajakta). Biswajit Das(Hiral Assistant 1). Barkha Fatnani(Hiral Assistant 2). Dibyendu Bhattacharya(Medical Examiner 1 (Anjali)). Sanjay Dev(Medical Examiner 2 (Rohan)). Ankita Goraya(Lead Actress). Apurva Chaudhari(Sujata). Aparna Upadhyay(Judge (Session Court)). Pavni Mehrotra(Sunaina (Law Student)). Aparajit Singh(Ankur (Law Student)). Chirag Tawarmalani(Apoorva). Nikita Salve(Vaishali). Bhakti Patharey(TV Reporter 1). Ria Sidwani(TV Reporter 2). Anuj Khurana(TV Reporter 3). Tabu(TV Reporter 4). Mahi Sharma(Gayatri (Kainaz Collegue)). Riva Arora(Roshni (Tarun’s Daughter)). 

Language Hindi.

Producers Murli Chhatwani. Aditya Chowksey. Amit Dalmia. Sanjay Inamdar. Sanjeev Joshi. Manoj Kumar. Santosh K. Mishra. Abhishek Pathak. Kumar Mangat Pathak. Vignesh Shetty. Shreya Dev Verma.

Production Panorama Studios. T-Series.
